data.description: Brick front home on cul-de-sac lot.  5 bedrooms 4 bathrooms nearly 4000 sqft home.  On main level you have foyer entry, formal dining room, office/den/flex space, great room with fireplace, large kitchen with eat in dining area, pantry, and a 1st floor guest room plus full bathroom.  On second level you will find the primary bedroom with sitting area, attached ensuite bathroom and large closet, additional 3 bedrooms one with attached bathroom, and another flex/bonus space.  Back yard is fully privacy fenced with protected wetlands behind, and covered porch.
